  "title": "Sour Russian Porridge Oats Pudding",
  "description": "A traditional Russian breakfast dish made with sour porridge oats, binchotan-charcoal powder, and other wholesome ingredients. This recipe is perfect for those looking for a comforting, healthy, and shojin-friendly meal.",
