  "instructions": [
    "Combine porridge oats, sour cream, sugar, and salt in a medium saucepan.",
    "Gradually add water and bring the mixture to a boil over medium heat.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10-15 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add milk, binchotan-charcoal powder, and vegan vanilla extract. Mix well.",
    "If desired, sprinkle flaxseeds on top for added nutrition.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, or until the mixture thickens slightly.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool for a few minutes.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional sour cream or sugar if desired."
